M||tx|---
M|Boy |tx|> "Always leave the codebase cleaner than you found it."
M|Boy |Attr|Robert C. Martin (Uncle Bob)
M|Core|tx|Make small improvements continuously. Do not wait for dedicated refactoring sprints. Incremental improvement prevents rot. Compounding effect over time.
M|Deci|When|
M|Deci|tx|\| Claim tp \| Critique Question \|
M|Deci|tx|\|------------\|-------------------\|
M|Deci|tx|\| "While fixing this, I shd also..." \| Is the additional work within the touched area? \|
M|Deci|tx|\| "This needs refactoring first" \| Can the fix proceed w/o the rf? \|
M|Deci|tx|\| "I'll clean this up while I'm here" \| Will cleanup delay delivery? \|
M|Boun|When|
M|Boun|tx|\| VERIFIED \| FAILED \| UNCERTAIN \|
M|Boun|tx|\|----------\|--------\|-----------\|
M|Boun|tx|\| Change is in touched code area \| Change unrelated to current work \| Scope unclear from context \|
M|Boun|tx|\| Small, safe improvement \| Large refactoring bundled w/ fix \| Risk assessment missing \|
M|Boun|tx|\| Balanced w/ delivery \| Perfectionism blocking progress \| Trade-offs not articulated \|
M|Warn|Duri|
M|Warn|it|"While I'm here" expanding to major work
M|Warn|it|Scope creep in PRs
M|Warn|it|Delivery blk by improvement claims
M|Warn|it|No clear connection btw improvement and original goal
M|Synt|When|
M|Synt|- **|Improvement clearly scoped to touched area, safe, and not blocking delivery
M|Synt|- **|Scope unclear or trade-offs not addressed; needs boundary clarification
M|Synt|- **|Large refactoring masquerading as small improvement; requires separate planning
M|Rela|- **|Understand before changing
M|Rela|- **|Incremental migration for larger changes